import { InfoWrapper, Form, Button, Label, Text } from "./Searchbar.styled"

export const Searchbar = () => {

	return (
		<InfoWrapper class="searchbar">
			<Form class="form">
				<Button type="submit" class="button">
					<Label class="button-label">Search</Label>
				</Button>

				<Text
					class="input"
					type="text"
					autocomplete="off"
					autofocus
					placeholder="Search images and photos"
				/>
			</Form>
		</InfoWrapper>
	)
}
